"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-paris-2024-2024-0724-1461542-im-here-for-business-clancy-settles-into-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sligo boxer Dean Clancy feels far from overawed having settled into life at the Paris Olympics as he awaits the draw on Thursday evening.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 5, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"score\": 0.9999936090111575, \"rank\": 6.295701998011413e-06, \"text\": \"Sligo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\"}, {\"begin\": 12, \"end\": 16, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.999999998111889, \"rank\": 1.8494093469079804e-09, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_Clancy\", \"score\": 0.9997159178889461, \"rank\": 0.00022189761074706545, \"text\": \"Clancy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_Clancy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_Clancy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 68, \"to\": 72}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 76, \"to\": 94}, {\"ngram\": \"the draw\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 116}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday evening\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 22, Clancy comes into the tournament as a first-time Olympian and is the present and future of the sport for Ireland.\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 195, \"end\": 203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999924712029, \"rank\": 7.509438314758416e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 251, \"end\": 258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999947008291, \"rank\": 5.2990205071362906e-09, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clancy\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 152}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 178}, {\"ngram\": \"future\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A rising star, he has set his sights on a medal early in his career.\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his sights\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 308}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the sheer scale of the Olympics is something to behold, he believes a life in the sport has prepared him for this day.\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sheer scale\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"a life\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 411}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"this day\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to RT\\u00c9 Sport, Clancy said: \\\"I had to pinch myself when I was waking up in Olympic Village, it's amazing.\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999998799467, \"rank\": 1.1999561005040315e-10, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"Clancy\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a surreal moment, it's been a long time waiting, and to finally be here, I am really excited.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 669, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a surreal moment\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have to remind myself to be grateful to be in the position I am in.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the position\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have trained our whole life to get here.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 785, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our whole life\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just soaking it all up and staying focused on waiting for the draw Thursday evening and taking it one fight at a time.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the draw\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"one fight\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went to Buenos Aires for the Youth Olympics, I have an idea about this whole atmosphere of different sports and stuff, but it's just amazing.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"score\": 0.9999990301444242, \"rank\": 9.428529429670039e-07, \"text\": \"Buenos Aires\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Youth Olympics\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"an idea\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"this whole atmosphere\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"different sports\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is really surreal.\\\"\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kellie Harrington, Aoife O'Rourke and Michaela and Aoife Walsh have been offering pearls of wisdom when called upon.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1080, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kellie Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\"}, {\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aoife_O'Rourke\", \"score\": 0.9999999048045584, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aoife O'Rourke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aoife_O'Rourke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aoife_O'Rourke\"}, {\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michaela_McQueen\", \"score\": 0.9981422295795347, \"rank\": 0.0018612239586949918, \"text\": \"Michaela\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michaela_McQueen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michaela_McQueen\"}, {\"begin\": 1131, \"end\": 1142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aoife_Walsh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aoife Walsh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aoife_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aoife_Walsh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pearls\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"wisdom\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have the knowledge of the Olympics experience, something Clancy is keen to draw on.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the knowledge\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics experience\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"Clancy\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no better people to have around us than likes of Kelly, Aidan, Michaela and Aoife.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1361, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michaela_McQueen\", \"score\": 0.9981422295795347, \"rank\": 0.0018612239586949918, \"text\": \"Michaela\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michaela_McQueen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michaela_McQueen\"}, {\"begin\": 1374, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aoife_MacMurrough\", \"score\": 0.9999333210574767, \"rank\": 6.668328353040407e-05, \"text\": \"Aoife\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aoife_MacMurrough\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aoife_MacMurrough\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no better people\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"likes\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"Kelly\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"Aidan\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are just perfect examples of high-performance athletes and they have been there and done that and any advice I can get off them [is very worthwhile].\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"perfect examples\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"high-performance athletes\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"any advice\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am only 22 myself so it's great to be surrounded by people like that, that have been there and dealt with it and been in this atmosphere and this experience and this setting before.\\\"\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only 22 myself\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1600}, {\"ngram\": \"this atmosphere\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1678}, {\"ngram\": \"this experience\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clancy's mindset has been to take the occasion away from his performances in the tournament if possible, and simply take it on as another event.\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clancy's mindset\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"the occasion\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1772}, {\"ngram\": \"his performances\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"another event\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Easier said than done, and he does not want to get lost in the ring when the enormity of the experience is surrounding him.\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Easier\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"the enormity\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Defeat can leave his tournament over in a matter of minutes, so his eyes are firmly on the prize.\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Defeat\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"his tournament\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"a matter\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"minutes\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"his eyes\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2069}, {\"ngram\": \"the prize\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That is kind of the way I have always looked at most tournaments,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kind of the way\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"most tournaments\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think we are always in a ring and we are always fighting someone, whether that's sparring or competition or whatever it is.\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2305, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a ring\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I am just going to look at it as a normal tournament and not putting too much pressure on myself.\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a normal tournament\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"too much pressure\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then it's just going to fight.\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been boxing and fighting my whole life, so that's the kind of the way I want to look at it.\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my whole life\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"the kind\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Regardless of the lights and the noise, get in there and take one round and one fight at a time.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2639, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lights\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2567}, {\"ngram\": \"the noise\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"one round\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"one fight\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2628}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You get the gameplan off coaches for whoever we are fighting against and just implement that and go out there and for me have fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gameplan\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2660}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"whoever\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2684}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Passing the time in the village is not a problem and the self-appointed title of 'head barista' while making coffee for his team-mates is one duty to help that.\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2804}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2821}, {\"ngram\": \"the self-appointed title\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2850}, {\"ngram\": \"head barista\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2867}, {\"ngram\": \"coffee\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"his team-mates\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"one duty\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 2919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he is also learning being around different sports, speaking to other athletes and taking nuggets of information about their preparations.\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"different sports\", \"from\": 2972, \"to\": 2988}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"nuggets\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3035}, {\"ngram\": \"information\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3050}, {\"ngram\": \"their preparations\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The draw for the boxing tournament is on Thursday, something which is a frustration for some, but Clancy is unperturbed by that.\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The draw\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"the boxing tournament\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 3119, \"to\": 3127}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3138}, {\"ngram\": \"a frustration\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3161}, {\"ngram\": \"Clancy\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no agony at all.\", \"from\": 3208, \"to\": 3234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no agony\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few people have said 'oh is the draw not done', but most tournaments we go to it's only a matter of days beforehand where the draw is done.\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A few people\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3247}, {\"ngram\": \"the draw\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3273}, {\"ngram\": \"only a matter\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3333}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3341}, {\"ngram\": \"the draw\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having an extra few days here means we can settle in.\", \"from\": 3378, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an extra few days\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's such a large scale here that there is things to do.\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a large scale\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3456}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can get a routine and wait for the draw.\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a routine\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3510}, {\"ngram\": \"the draw\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The team are all ready, we all know what to do, and we are all just waiting for the job, waiting for when we are in and when to go to action.\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The team\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3544}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3623}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 3670, \"to\": 3676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When that comes we are going to be at our the best.\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we are all inour best possible shape we have ever been.\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"best possible shape\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am here for business and here for a medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"business\", \"from\": 3808, \"to\": 3816}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch the 2024 Olympic Games with 14 hours of televised action on RT\\u00c92 and RT\\u00c9 Player each day.\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3907, \"end\": 3911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"score\": 0.9994238889060038, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c92\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3847, \"to\": 3869}, {\"ngram\": \"14 hours\", \"from\": 3875, \"to\": 3883}, {\"ngram\": \"televised action\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3903}, {\"ngram\": \"RT\\u00c9 Player\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 3926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Listen to extensive radio coverage on RT\\u00c9 Radio 1 and 2fm's Game On and follow each moment from Paris on RT\\u00c9.ie, the RT\\u00c9 News app and all RT\\u00c9 digital platforms.\", \"from\": 3937, \"to\": 4097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4033, \"end\": 4038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999986926014, \"rank\": 1.3073437235522913e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http